author: kotkov
msg: Fix a segfault occuring when svn_stream_read_full() or svn_stream_skip() are
called for a no-op stream created using svn_stream_create().  Instead of
crashing, these scenarios should gracefully return an expected error
(svn_stream_create): Do not forget to zero out the 'read_full_fn' member.

author: philip
msg: Extract the httpd version at configure time rather than in
davautocheck.sh, pass --httpd-version as a testsuite option
rather than using the environment SVNTEST_HTTPD_VERSION.
This is how other test flags support both 'make check' and
(HTTPD_VERSION): Set value, based on code from davautocheck.sh.
